title: "GH-651: pm activity bare relative windows silently return empty results"
description: "GitHub issue #651 reports that pm activity --from accepts plausible bare relative windows such as 7d, 1w, P7D, and now-7d but returns an empty success response, while -7d works and other invalid strings fail loudly. Normalize bare lower-bound windows to ago semantics or reject them consistently with an actionable grammar hint; document the accepted relative syntax."
